Thanks everyone.  It took me about 5 years to put it together.  I really wasn't trying to collect graded or ungraded cards so I have a mix of both but have mostly ungraded.  I bought most of the cards here (probably about 80% of them) and bought a lot of about 200 cards once which really helped.
